 ![单行文本溢出](/AnastasiaJ/uploads/单行溢出.jpg)

html
```
<div class="test">This is some long text that will not fit in the box</div>
```

css
```
div.test{
	white-space:nowrap; 
	width:12em; 
	overflow:hidden; 
	border:1px solid #000000;
    text-overflow:ellipsis;
}
```

